### Tests API Account Management - Version Simple
### Pour tester rapidement les fonctionnalités de base

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@deviceId = test-device-123

### 1. Test basique - Récupérer les comptes
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/account-management
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "get_accounts",
  "data": {
    "deviceId": "{{deviceId}}"
  }
}

###

### 2. Test de sauvegarde (sans token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/account-management
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "save_account",
  "data": {
    "deviceId": "{{deviceId}}",
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "nom": "Test",
    "prenom": "User"
  }
}

###

### 3. Test de vérification PIN
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/account-management
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "verify_pin",
  "data": {
    "deviceId": "{{deviceId}}",
    "userId": "test@example.com",
    "pin": "123456"
  }
}

###

### 4. Test d'action invalide
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/account-management
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "invalid_action",
  "data": {}
}

###

